Sí.

00:26:05.689 --> 00:26:07.274
Lloraste en mi sueño.

00:26:16.992 --> 00:26:18.493
Lloré contigo.

00:26:29.546 --> 00:26:32.090
LEY HAEKWANG

00:26:32.173 --> 00:26:33.717
CHOI DAM-DONG

00:26:43.643 --> 00:26:45.812
Sr. Choi, le traje café.

